title: Gospel Gangstaz - Gang Affiliated
description:
Gang Affiliated is the debut album released by Gospel Gangstaz. It was released on February 28, 1995 for MXY Records and featured production from DJ Dove and Mr. Solo. Gang Affiliated managed to make it to 19 on the Top Christian Albums Billboard chart, however the three singles, "Mobbin&#039; (Gang Affiliated)", "Testimony" and "Y Cain&#039;t da Homiez Hear Me?" did not make it to any billboard charts.
